idata.python:
rest ( beats= 31)
def mainbeat(snare = 2, kick = 0):
    playNote(kick, 0.75)
    playNote(snare, beats = 0.25)
    playNote(kick, beats = 0.5)
    playNote(snare, beats = 0.5)
    playNote(kick, beats = 0.75)
    playNote(snare, beats = 0.25)
    playNote(kick, beats = 0.5)
    playNote(snare, beats = 0.5)
    
for i in range(6):
    mainbeat(kick = None)
                   
for i in range(10):
    mainbeat()
